Ask HN: Email SaaS
text:
If you had to build an email marketing platform from scratch, or close to scratch, how would you go about it?

Like, how would you build a SendX (https://www.sendx.io/) with a feature-set including the following a) Email editor with ready-made templates b) Recipient segmentation within a web app c) Message scheduling/automation d) Performance monitoring

I'm not talking about the tech stack as much as the email server bit...where can I learn a bit more about that?
